# Rust Standards

## Style & quality
- Edition 2021; run `cargo fmt` and `cargo clippy -- -D warnings` before commit.
- Follow [Rust API Guidelines](https://rust-lang.github.io/api-guidelines/) for public `core` API.
- Use `#[serde(rename_all = "snake_case")]` for config enums (existing convention).

## Errors
- Library (`core`): `BolootError` via `thiserror`, never `anyhow`.
- Binaries (`cli`, `daemon`): `anyhow::Result` at top level with `.context()`.

## Testing
- Unit tests in `core` for calendar conversion, format, locale, prayer.
- Use golden dates (e.g. Nowruz 1404 = 2025-03-20) and property tests for round-trip.
- Add D-Bus integration tests for `daemon` when touching `dbus_iface.rs`.

## Dependencies
- Prefer workspace deps in root `Cargo.toml`.
- Audit with `cargo-audit`; license check with `cargo-deny` (GPL-3.0-or-later).
